# ============================================================================
# DIRECTORY: db/migrations/versions/
# ============================================================================
#
# PURPOSE:
#   Contains Alembic migration version scripts. Each file represents a
#   database schema change with upgrade() and downgrade() functions.
#
# EXPECTED MIGRATIONS:
#   - 001_create_sessions_table.py    → CREATE TABLE sessions
#   - 002_create_tasks_table.py       → CREATE TABLE tasks
#   - 003_create_agent_logs_table.py  → CREATE TABLE agent_logs
#   - 004_create_user_preferences.py  → CREATE TABLE user_preferences
#   - (future migrations as schema evolves)
#
# ============================================================================
